# Privacy Policy

Last updated: 4-13-26

## Who this applies to

This policy covers the "World Cup Tourism Surge | InfiniteRestaurants.ai"
Custom GPT published on ChatGPT, and the Infinite Restaurants website at
infiniterestaurants.ai.

## What we collect

We do not collect personal data through the Custom GPT. Your conversations
with the GPT happen inside ChatGPT and are governed by OpenAI's privacy
policy (https://openai.com/policies/privacy-policy).

The Custom GPT fetches a single public file from our website
(https://www.infiniterestaurants.ai/llms.txt). That fetch is a standard web
request and does not send us any information about who you are or what you
asked.

If you contact us directly by email, we retain that email only to respond
to you. We do not use email contact information for marketing.

## What we do not do

We do not:
- Receive or store the contents of your ChatGPT conversations
- Track you across sites
- Sell data to third parties
- Use cookies or analytics on the Custom GPT (we don't have that ability —
  conversations happen inside ChatGPT, not on our site)

## Third parties

The Custom GPT runs on OpenAI's platform and is subject to OpenAI's privacy
practices. Anything you type into the GPT is handled by OpenAI.

